-- 
IWC to Expand Watch Production in Switzerland, Blick Reports

-- B y   L e i g h   B a l d w i n
-- 
2011-12-03T13:06:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-03/iwc-to-expand-watch-production-in-switzerland-blick-reports.html
International Watch Co., owned by  Cie
Financiere Richemont SA (CFR) , plans to expand production in
 Switzerland ,  Blick  said, without saying where it got the
information.  The Swiss watchmaker will spend 2.9 million francs ($3.1
million) to expand offices in Schaffhausen and will acquire
20,000 square meters of manufacturing space in Merishausertal,
the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Leigh Baldwin in Zurich at 
 lbaldwin3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  